Description: This is a simple framework developed on libqglviewer2.5.3 and qt 4.8 for displaying 3D object. Any complex GUI can be developed on this basic framwork.
Author: sway
Time: 11/05/2014
Organization: Institute of Automation, Chinese Academy of Science


==============================================================================
simpleViewer.h :define a Viewer class for viewing 3D objects

simpleViewer.cpp: implement related class memembers of class Viewer

main.cpp: run the class
